  - '"if you give me carrots, i''ll get working."'
  - '"Scouts honor."'
  - '"So you in or no?"'
  - '"Haha, don''t be like that"'
  - '"Why dont you buy some carrot seeds with the coins i''ve given you?"'
  - '"The trader should be at the bridge by now."'
  - '"The trader should be at the bridge by now."'
  - '"Did you get the seeds?"'
  - '"A promise is a promise, let''s get working."'
